name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: yarn.app.mapreduce.am.scheduler.heartbeat.interval-ms
description:
The interval in ms at which the MR AppMaster should send
    heartbeats to the ResourceManager

name: dfs.qjournal.get-journal-state.timeout.ms
description:
Timeout in milliseconds when calling getJournalState().
    JournalNodes.

name: dfs.datanode.lazywriter.interval.sec
description: Interval in seconds for Datanodes for lazy persist writes.

name: dfs.namenode.edit.log.autoroll.check.interval.ms
description:
How often an active namenode will check if it needs to roll its edit log,
    in milliseconds.

name: fs.ftp.host.port
description: FTP filesystem connects to fs.ftp.host on this port

name: dfs.namenode.resource.du.reserved
description:
The amount of space to reserve/require for a NameNode storage directory
    in bytes. The default is 100MB. Support multiple size unit
    suffix(case insensitive), as described in dfs.blocksize.
